      "path": "audio/narrations/nbody-simulation/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "夜空中的每一颗星，都在被其它所有天体拉扯着。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nbody-simulation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nbody-simulation/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.52,
      "size": 24336,
      "text": "这种彼此牵引的运动，就是 N 体引力问题。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nbody-simulation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nbody-simulation/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38016,
      "text": "规则简单到只有一条万有引力定律，结果却可以复杂到无法预测。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nbody-simulation",
      "section_id": "law",
      "line_id": "law-1",
      "filename": "law-law-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nbody-simulation/yunxi/law-law-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "任意两个质点之间的引力，正比于它们质量的乘积，反比于距离的平方。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nbody-simulation",
      "section_id": "law",
      "line_id": "law-2",
      "filename": "law-law-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nbody-simulation/yunxi/law-law-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "每个天体受到的合力，是其它所有天体引力的向量叠加。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nbody-simulation",
      "section_id": "law",
      "line_id": "law-3",
      "filename": "law-law-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nbody-simulation/yunxi/law-law-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "把合力除以质量得到加速度，就能一步步推进整个系统的运动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nbody-simulation",
      "section_id": "twobody",
      "line_id": "two-1",
      "filename": "twobody-two-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nbody-simulation/yunxi/twobody-two-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.83,
      "size": 29232,
      "text": "当系统里只有两个天体时，问题可以被完全解出来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nbody-simulation",
      "section_id": "twobody",
      "line_id": "two-2",
      "filename": "twobody-two-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nbody-simulation/yunxi/twobody-two-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "它们绕着共同的质心运动，轨道是规整的椭圆或圆。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nbody-simulation",
      "section_id": "twobody",
      "line_id": "two-3",
      "filename": "twobody-two-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nbody-simulation/yunxi/twobody-two-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.16,
      "size": 34560,
      "text": "这就是行星绕恒星、月亮绕地球背后那份可预测的优雅。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nbody-simulation",
      "section_id": "chaos",
      "line_id": "chaos-1",
      "filename": "chaos-chaos-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nbody-simulation/yunxi/chaos-chaos-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.74,
      "size": 27792,
      "text": "可一旦加进第三个天体，情况就彻底改变了。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nbody-simulation",
      "section_id": "chaos",
      "line_id": "chaos-2",
      "filename": "chaos-chaos-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nbody-simulation/yunxi/chaos-chaos-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "三体问题没有一般的解析解，绝大多数轨道都是混沌的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nbody-simulation",
      "section_id": "chaos",
      "line_id": "chaos-3",
      "filename": "chaos-chaos-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nbody-simulation/yunxi/chaos-chaos-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.25,
      "size": 36000,
      "text": "初始位置哪怕只差万分之一，长期演化也会截然不同。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nbody-simulation",
      "section_id": "chaos",
      "line_id": "chaos-4",
