      "path": "audio/narrations/nbody-simulation/yunxi/chaos-chaos-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "只有少数特殊的初值，才能走出像八字这样的周期性轨道。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nbody-simulation",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nbody-simulation/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.45,
      "size": 39168,
      "text": "切换不同的预设，看双星、恒星行星和三体各自如何演化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nbody-simulation",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/nbody-simulation/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "留意屏幕上的总能量，好的数值积分会让它始终保持稳定。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "nbody-simulation",
      "section_id": "summary",
